* My ex-wife
was very cruel *

11:06.934 --> 11:09.069
* Bordering on shrewish

11:09.102 --> 11:11.471
* But luckily for all of you

11:11.504 --> 11:13.707
* She happened to be Jewish

11:13.741 --> 11:15.776
* We never really
talked at all *

11:15.809 --> 11:18.145
* I barely ever laid her

11:18.178 --> 11:20.147
* But I did get
one thing out of it *

11:20.180 --> 11:22.850
* I learned to make a seder

11:22.883 --> 11:24.752
* She doesn't know
which foods to buy *

11:24.785 --> 11:26.920
* She doesn't know
what to fixah *

11:26.954 --> 11:29.156
* She needs someone
to help her out *

11:29.189 --> 11:31.391
* I'm just a silly shiksa

11:31.424 --> 11:33.493
BARNEY:
* It really is quite simple

11:33.526 --> 11:35.763
* You cook and tell a story

11:35.796 --> 11:37.731
* The food will
give you heartburn *

11:37.765 --> 11:40.167
* The tale is very gory

11:40.200 --> 11:42.502
* Let's eat
* Let's eat

11:42.535 --> 11:44.738
* Let's have a seder

11:44.772 --> 11:46.874
* First we'll tell the story

11:46.907 --> 11:48.776
* And we'll have
the dinner later *

11:50.911 --> 11:53.346
* Pharaoh was
a great big jerk *

11:53.380 --> 11:55.348
* He told the Jews
to get to work *

11:55.382 --> 11:58.051
* But Moses had God
on his side *

11:58.085 --> 12:00.020
* Bada-bing, infanticide

