that... what-what...

14:18.191 --> 14:20.227
what was it?
The seminar for enhancing
your memory?

14:20.260 --> 14:22.029
Yeah, I think that was it.
(groaning)

14:22.062 --> 14:23.430
Look, the point is

14:23.463 --> 14:26.066
I'm a quitter because
my dad never taught me

14:26.099 --> 14:27.267
